</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Views" /><category term="Clouds" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Stopping to take a picture of the beautiful view in Arashiyama this morning. Me too. 今朝、嵐山で美しい景色を写真に収めるために足を止めた。私も。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2605_A7R01543.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2605_A7R01543.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">So Green・とても緑豊か</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260507/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="So Green・とても緑豊か" /><published>2026-05-07T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-05-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/green</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260507/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
